✨ Awards come and go, but the trust I’ve built? That’s timeless.
From 2021 to 2024 — every recognition is a reflection of your love, my dedication, and the artistry we created together.

🏆 WedMeGood User’s Choice Winner – 2021, 2022, 2023
🏆 Cosmopolitan Blogger Awards 2024–25
🏆 National Excellence Honour – Bengaluru

These awards aren’t just trophies — they are reminders of why I started, and how far I’ve come.

Thank you to every bride, student, and soul who believed in me.

💄 Still growing. Still glowing. 

📍 Bangalore | Bridal | Airbrush | Academy
📞 Bookings & Training: 8197551799

#parulkhattarmakeupartist #awardwinningmua #bridalmakeupbangalore #makeupjourney #southindianbride #airbrushmakeup #makeupacademyindia #luxurybridallook

Never imagined that I would go on to win the Cosmopolitan award. To top that, today, I have attended the @cosmoindia editors lunch in Mumbai with an extremely talented bunch of professionals accompanied by delicious and scrumptious food @kmcmumbai Thoroughly enjoyed this well organized event. This is indeed a dream, one that I am living queensize, that has come true in every sense of the word.

Thank you so much, @cosmoindia , @pratishtha_dobhal @sonalved 

#cosmpolitanindia #editorslunch #funfilledday😍

I am so thrilled to receive the emerging makeup artist-south award from  @cosmoindia , @lovecolorbar 🥰🥰. I am grateful to them for providing such a great platform ♥️♥️♥️🥰. 

Again, thanks to all my clients, co-workers,  friends, and family.
